                        <span class="accordion-icon text-sky-700 text-xl">▼</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content bg-white p-4 rounded-b-lg">
                         <p class="mb-3">This part of the plan focuses on strengthening customer bonds by aligning with the retention team for enhanced lifecycle flows and refining customer segmentation, especially for collectors and high-value buyers.</p>
                        <h4 class="text-md font-semibold mt-3 mb-2">1. Aligning with Retention Team for Enhanced Flows & Winback Sequences</h4>
                        <p>Collaboration with the retention team will optimize customer lifecycle flows and implement new winback sequences. Focus areas:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-3">
                            <li><strong>Hyper-Personalization at Scale:</strong> Tailor messaging using granular customer data.</li>
                            <li><strong>Gamification & Loyalty Programs:</strong> Explore VIP programs with points, tiers, and exclusive rewards for collectors.</li>
                            <li><strong>Automated Re-engagement Campaigns:</strong> Sophisticated, personalized sequences for inactive customers.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Retention efforts will extend to fostering community engagement via platforms like Discord, rewarding contributions, and building a sense of belonging.</p>

                        <h4 class="text-md font-semibold mt-3 mb-2">2. Advanced Customer Segmentation for Collectors & High-Value Buyers</h4>
                        <p>Customer segmentation will be refined to incorporate deeper behavioral and psychographic insights. Key segments:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-3">
                            <li>"Drop VIPs"</li>
                            <li>"IP Loyalists"</li>
                            <li>"Aesthetic Aficionados"</li>
                            <li>"Early Adopters/Hype Chasers"</li>
                            <li>"High-LTV Collectors"</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>This advanced segmentation will enable hyper-personalized communication and targeted marketing campaigns, increasing engagement and conversion rates.</p>
                    </div>
