                        <h4 class="text-md font-semibold mt-3 mb-2">1. Optimize Budget Allocation Based on Blended MER, Incremental Revenue, & Campaign Performance</h4>
                        <p>Budget allocation will be dynamically optimized:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-3">
                            <li><strong>MER-Based Budgeting:</strong> Use "Blended MER" as a primary indicator for overall marketing effectiveness.</li>
                            <li><strong>Incremental Revenue Attribution:</strong> Implement models to understand true additional revenue from marketing.</li>
                            <li><strong>Dynamic Reallocation:</strong> Regularly review performance to reallocate budget to higher-performing initiatives.</li>
                            <li><strong>Strategic Budgeting for Drops:</strong> Allocate significantly to pre-launch hype, direct response, and influencers.</li>
