                        <h4 class="text-md font-semibold mt-3 mb-2">2. Work Cross-Functionally with Creative, Product, & Ecommerce to Roadmap Seasonal Growth Pushes</h4>
                        <p>Deep cross-functional collaboration will be fostered:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mb-3">
                            <li><strong>Integrated Planning:</strong> Marketing involved early in product roadmap discussions.</li>
                            <li><strong>Creative Alignment:</strong> Close collaboration with Creative for on-brand, high-quality assets.</li>
                            <li><strong>Product-Marketing Synergy:</strong> Translate technical features into compelling customer benefits.</li>
                            <li><strong>Ecommerce Readiness:</strong> Partner with Ecommerce to prepare website infrastructure for traffic surges.</li>
                            <li><strong>Shared Goals & Metrics:</strong> Establish shared OKRs across teams for major launches.</li>
